= View My Submissions

- Epic: Student Progress Tracking
- Actor: Student
- MVP: No
- BR: BR20
- Description / Notes: Track my past work
- As a: Student
- I want to: See my submissions
- So that: I can monitor my learning
- Trigger: The student navigates to the "My Submissions" page.
- Pre-condition:
    - The student is logged in.
- Post-condition:
    - A list of the student's submissions is displayed with their status and feedback.
- Solution (Step-by-Step):
  - Open "My Submissions" page
  - Fetch list of submissions
  - Show status and feedback